Metadata.value:
With meta as (Select 
'@{pipeline().DataFactory}' as DataFactory_Name,

'@{activity('ACT_GEN_META_TargetFile').output.columnCount}' as ColumnCount,
'@{activity('ACT_MT_Copy_SQL_To_ADLS').output.rowsCopied}' as [RowCount],
'@{activity('ACT_MT_Copy_SQL_To_ADLS').output.effectiveIntegrationRuntime}' as IntegrationRuntime,
'@{activity('ACT_MT_Copy_SQL_To_ADLS').output.executionDetails[0].source.type}' as Source_Type,
'@{activity('ACT_MT_Copy_SQL_To_ADLS').output.executionDetails[0].sink.type}' as Sink_Type,
'@{activity('ACT_MT_Copy_SQL_To_ADLS').output.executionDetails[0].status}' as Execution_Status,
'@{pipeline().parameters.Data_Source_Table_Name}' as 'PipelineParameters.Data_Source_Table_Name',
'@{pipeline().parameters.Data_Source_WaterMarkColumn}' as 'PipelineParameters.Data_Source_WaterMarkColumn',
'@{pipeline().parameters.Data_Source_Instance}' as 'PipelineParameters.Data_Source_Instance',
'@{pipeline().parameters.Data_Source_Database}' as 'PipelineParameters.Data_Source_Database',
'@{pipeline().parameters.Data_Destination_Zone_Container}' as 'PipelineParameters.Data_Destination_Zone_Container',
'@{pipeline().parameters.Data_Destination_Directory}' as 'PipelineParameters.Data_Destination_Directory',
'@{pipeline().parameters.Project_Name}' as 'PipelineParameters.Project_Name',
'@{pipeline().parameters.Solution_Name}' as 'PipelineParameters.Solution_Name',
'@{pipeline().parameters.Data_Source_Object_Name}' as 'PipelineParameters.Data_Source_Object_Name',
'@{pipeline().parameters.Data_Destination_Filename}' as 'PipelineParameters.Data_Destination_Filename',
'@{pipeline().parameters.Storage_Account_Name}' as 'PipelineParameters.Storage_Account_Name'
) Select m.*, Attribute.SourceSystem as 'Attribute.SourceSystem', Attribute.PII as 'Attribute.PII', Attribute.Tags as 'Attribute.Tags' from meta m
CROSS JOIN (select [SourceSystem], [PII], [Tags] from (Select JSON_QUERY(REPLACE('@{json(string(pipeline().parameters.attributes))}',char(92),''),'$') attribute) q Cross Apply OpenJson(q.attribute) With ([SourceSystem] varchar(200) '$.SourceSystem',[PII] bit '$.PII',[Tags]  varchar(200) '$.Tags')) as Attribute
